          Personalized 1-on-1 classes for kids and adults — flexible timings,
          Al-Azhar certified instructors, and expert guidance from day one.
        </p>

        <!-- Spec 3: CTA group — primary + secondary -->
        <div class="hero-cta-group">

          <!-- Primary CTA: "Book Free Trial", #28A745, 14px 28px, radius 10–12px -->
          <a href="#book-trial"
             class="hero-btn-primary"
             data-track="hero-primary-cta"
             aria-label="Book a free trial class — no credit card required">
            📅 Book Free Trial
            <span class="btn-free-tag" aria-hidden="true">FREE</span>
          </a>

          <!-- Secondary CTA: "Watch Demo", outline style -->
          <a href="#demo"
             class="hero-btn-secondary"
             data-track="hero-secondary-cta">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"
                 aria-hidden="true" style="flex-shrink:0;">
              <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2"/>
              <path d="M6.5 5.5l5 2.5-5 2.5V5.5z" fill="currentColor"/>
            </svg>
            Watch Demo
          </a>

        </div>

        <!-- Spec 4: Micro trust text — "Free Trial • No Credit Card Required" -->
        <p class="hero-micro-trust" aria-label="No credit card required">
          ✓ Free Trial &nbsp;•&nbsp; ✓ No Credit Card Required &nbsp;•&nbsp; ✓ Cancel Anytime
        </p>

        <!-- Spec 5: Trust signal row — ⭐ 4.9  👨‍🏫 50+ Teachers  🌍 Global Students -->
        <div class="hero-trust-row" aria-label="Trust signals">

          <div class="htr-item">
            <span class="htr-icon" aria-hidden="true">⭐</span>
            <span class="htr-text">
              <strong>4.9/5</strong> Rating
            </span>
          </div>

          <span class="htr-divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>

          <div class="htr-item">
            <span class="htr-icon" aria-hidden="true">👨‍🏫</span>
            <span class="htr-text">
              <strong>50+</strong> Teachers
            </span>
          </div>

          <span class="htr-divider" aria-hidden="true"></span>

          <div class="htr-item">
            <span class="htr-icon" aria-hidden="true">🌍</span>
            <span class="htr-text">
              <strong>10+</strong> Countries
            </span>
          </div>

        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial micro-card — social proof -->
        <div class="hero-testimonial-card" role="blockquote"
